nodes.text: A skirmish occurred in the planet Woteba when Luke Skywalker and Han Solo, along with C-3PO and R2-D2, attempted to combat at Fizz problem by tracking down five smugglers, one Neimoidian and four Aqualish, whom trade starship fuel to members of the Dark Nest for star amber.
